{"tid":2333552,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（我不想努力了）歐倩怡41歲仍然fit爆 晒腹肌線笑稱過度活躍","createTime":"2020-12-20T13:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T13:53:36.000Z","uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df50ecb0d729d13800086bb4cee43dc6d0e60304","tid":2333552,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:32:24.000Z","msg":"郭晉安老婆歐倩怡本月16日41歲生日，當日她在社交網貼上獨自對生日蛋糕照，留言：「生日，在忙碌中渡（度）過 在keep social distancing（保持社交距離）的時候，享受一下靜靜地渡（度）過吧！」<br />\n<br />\n童顏歐倩怡既是營養師又勤做運動，故仍保持少女Feel。<br />\n<br />\n身為一對子女的母親，歐倩怡擁有童顏面孔，加上積極操身形，仍保持少女feel。昨夜她大騷操練腹肌線的成果，還留言指要再增肌。<br />\n<br />\n她在ig story更上載十足細路女跳來跳去片段，自稱過度活躍的小朋友，怎看也不似41歲。<br />\n<br />\n巴士的報 唔俾link"},{"pid":"dd6a107ae474db3f7ca76ceb0516714e95fe20a2","tid":2333552,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:33:57.000Z","msg":"啊旺日日屌到佢仆街"},{"pid":"1bb669626621a376a7d12a6ceefb0d41b243b22d","tid":2333552,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/648p405/0x0/100/hd/a2547c51d431363ca0fe6d695408eb4e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201219/_2020121919541387018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F648p405%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fa2547c51d431363ca0fe6d695408eb4e%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201219%2F_2020121919541387018.jpg&h=950fdb74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n41歲似21喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67aab058ea7103896106ef9aa7252b6df3c6fab3","tid":2333552,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"微波版shinny"}]}